snippet.title: Overwatch 2 | Season 9 Gameplay & Competitive Breakdown
snippet.description:
Class is in session! Join mL7 and Eskay as they break down some of the gameplay and competitive changes coming to Overwatch 2 next season.

Check out these changes when Season 9: Champions launches Feb 13.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
_
